Im not sure why you would want this, but I made it a bit more &#x27;insane&#x27;<p>body,
body * {
  animation: insanity .001s infinite alternate cubic-bezier(0.455, 0.030, 0.515, 0.955);
}<p>@keyframes insanity {
  0% {
    margin: 0px 0 0 0;
  }
  25% {
    margin: 40px 20px 0 20px;
  }
  50% {
    margin: 0 20px 0 0;
  }
  75%{
    margin: -12px 12px 0 -1px;
  }
  100% {
    margin: 20px 0 0 0;
  }
}
